collectionMetadata.name: Number of Active CPF Members by Regrossed Balances & Age Group as at End of Year
collectionMetadata.description:
An active CPF member refers to a person who has at least 1 CPF employment contribution paid for him for the current or for any of the preceding 3 months. 

Regrossed balances include amounts withdrawn under Investment, Education, Residential Properties, Non-Residential Properties and Public Housing Schemes as at end of year. 

Figures exclude all self-employed persons. Figures are rounded to the nearest ten. 

"S" refers to number of active CPF members being less than 10 (for 2014) or 5 (from 2015 onwards).
